The,Language,Translator,API,translates,text,from,one,language,to,another,The,service,offers,multiple,domain,specific,models,that,you,can,customize,based,on,your,unique,terminology,and,language,Use,the,Language,Translator,to,take,news,from,across,the,globe,and,present,it,in,your,language,communicate,with,your,customers,in,their,own,language,and,more,It,includes,Translate,Identifiable,languages,Identify,language,List,models,and,more,The,IBM,Watson,Language,Translator,service,allows,you,to,create,an,application,that,identifies,the,language,of,input,text,and,uses,a,domain,specific,linguistic,model,to,translate,the,text,into,another,language